 BlinkIT Grocery Sales Analysis

 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes BlinkIT grocery sales data to understand customer behavior, product performance, and sales trends using Power BI.

 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze total sales
- Compare outlet performance
- Evaluate product categories
- Analyze customer ratings
- Identify sales trends

 🛠️ Tools Used

- Excel

 📊 KPIs

- Total Sales
- Average Sales
- Number of Items Sold
- Average Rating
- Outlet Performance
- Item Type Analysis

 📈 Insights

- Top-selling product categories
- Best-performing outlet locations
- Customer rating analysis
- Revenue contribution by outlet type
# 📂 Files

- BlinkIT Grocery Data.xlsx

